comment.author: 72347661@N02
comment._content:
The Picture is taken after the formation of the Swedish Air Force on July 1st, 1926.
It kept its permanent Army serial number 149. The first digit indicated building year in the Army (1925 and hence 5149) while the new digit 3 indicated its belonging, in this case tredje flygkåren (3rd Wing), hence 3149. In about May 1927 it recived a new serial number 066 and was written off on April 11th, 1929.
Stig
